==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Querl
<hw>Querl</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[G.
<ets>querlen</ets>, <ets>quirlen</ets>, to twirl, to turn round, fr.
<ets>querl</ets>, <ets>querl</ets>, a twirling stick. Cf.
<er>Twirl</er>.]</ety> <def>To twirl; to turn or wind round; to coil;
<as>as, to <ex>querl</ex> a cord, thread, or rope</as>.</def>
<mark>[Local, U.S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Querl</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Querl
<hw>Querl</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A coil; a twirl; <as>as, the
<ex>qwerl</ex> of hair on the fore leg of a blooded horse</as>.</def>
<mark>[Local, U. S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Quern</ent>⟦br⟧
